# marked export-ignore. The repo stays PRIVATE; these are internal artifacts that
# must never ship in a public snapshot. Keeping them here (rather than deleting)
# preserves them internally while guaranteeing they're absent from any release zip.
cli/AUDIT-TRIAD-KG-2026-05-21.md export-ignore
.github/ export-ignore
